## Anti-Patterns

### Code Constraints

**Block These Patterns:**
```rust
// ‚ùå FORBIDDEN - Bare SqliteStore (stores messages)
let store = SqliteStore::open_with_passphrase(...).await?;
let manager = Manager::load_registered(store).await?;

// ‚ùå FORBIDDEN - Old StromaProtocolStore (removed, never implemented Store trait)
let store = StromaProtocolStore::new(path, passphrase);
```

**Enforce These Patterns:**
```rust
// ‚úÖ REQUIRED - StromaStore wrapper (no-ops message persistence)
let store = StromaStore::open(db_path, passphrase).await?;
let manager = Manager::load_registered(store).await?;

// ‚úÖ REQUIRED - Ephemeral message handling
async fn handle_message(&mut self, message: Message) -> Result<()> {
    process_command(&message)?;
    // Message NOT stored - StromaStore no-ops save_message
    Ok(())
}
```

